244
00:17:58,925 --> 00:18:00,093
[gasps]

245
00:18:00,093 --> 00:18:01,201
[grunt]

246
00:18:02,268 --> 00:18:04,971
[grunts]

247
00:18:05,906 --> 00:18:07,440
Aiding and abetting
the enemy, eh?

248
00:18:07,440 --> 00:18:09,442
You guys really are
a pile of garbage!

249
00:18:09,475 --> 00:18:12,378
Chibi‐Usa! Let's transform!

250
00:18:15,549 --> 00:18:21,054
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>Moon Crisis Make Up!</i>

251
00:18:23,489 --> 00:18:33,567
<i>♪ Sailor Moon...</i>
<i>...Sailor Moon!♪</i>

252
00:18:33,567 --> 00:18:50,350
<i>♪ Sailor Moon...</i>
<i>...Sailor Moon!♪</i>

253
00:18:51,985 --> 00:18:55,155
