was taken to the dump!

254
00:18:55,155 --> 00:18:56,857
[small gasp]

255
00:18:57,323 --> 00:18:59,826
<i>(Sailor Mars)</i>
<i>Fire Soul!</i>

256
00:18:59,860 --> 00:19:01,602
Ai ai ai! Ow ow ow!
Thats hot!

257
00:19:01,635 --> 00:19:04,170
Take him out, girls!

258
00:19:04,505 --> 00:19:10,176
Please, Pegasus! Protect
everyone's dream!

259
00:19:12,478 --> 00:19:15,982
Twinkle Yell!

260
00:19:19,520 --> 00:19:22,956
[neigh]

261
00:19:36,637 --> 00:19:43,476
Moon Gorgeous Meditation!

262
00:19:55,589 --> 00:19:58,559
Stage Out!

263
00:20:14,280 --> 00:20:19,385
You saved both of our
lives just now...

264
00:20:19,452 --> 00:20:21,855
But why?

265
00:20:21,888 --> 00:20:25,358
Like I said, I envy you.

266
00:20:25,391 --> 00:20:28,361
To be so full of
dreams like that...

267
00:20:28,394 --> 00:20:32,533
[gasp] That girl... was you?

268
00:20:40,073 --> 00:20:41,141
[gasps]

269
00:20:42,042 --> 00:20:43,577
[gasps]

270
00:20:48,048 --> 00:20:50,050
Pegasus?

271
00:21:02,168 --> 00:21:03,504
[gasps]

272
00:21:03,537 --> 00:21:05,606
We have Dream Mirrors!

273
00:21:06,940 --> 00:21:11,411
Then that means...we did become
human after all....

274
00:21:11,444 --> 00:21:12,946
[happy chuckles]

275
00:21:19,052 --> 00:21:22,088
[gasps]

276
00:21:23,123 --> 00:21:27,060
No soul capable of dreaming
is ever truly lost.

277
00:21:27,093 --> 00:21:32,432
These three creatures, no, these
three humans... they will be
fine.

278
00:21:51,151 --> 00:21:54,555
It's time you girls
played your part.

279
00:21:54,588 --> 00:22:02,669
[giggling]

280
00:22:03,804 --> 00:22:07,641
Live here, in this
forest, and wait...

281
00:22:07,641 --> 00:22:12,245
For one day, the light will
return to this dark place.

