<i>What does it mean to become</i>
<i>a grown‐up?</i>

288
00:23:55,388 --> 00:23:58,291
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>It means getting one step closer</i>
<i>to achieving your dreams!</i>

289
00:23:58,358 --> 00:24:01,367
<i>(Chibi‐Usa)</i>
<i>But I met some kids today</i>
<i>who'd prefer to stay kids,</i>

290
00:24:01,401 --> 00:24:04,137
<i>...rather than work hard to</i>
<i>make their dreams come true.</i>

291
00:24:04,204 --> 00:24:08,642
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>What?! I tell you, kids these</i>
<i>days! They're always looking for</i>
<i>the easy route!</i>

292
00:24:08,709 --> 00:24:15,281
